## Comprehensive Codebase Exploration Report: Long-Running Harness DAW

### Project Overview
This is a **browser-based DAW (Digital Audio Workstation)** built with:
- **Frontend**: React 19 + TypeScript + Zustand (state management)
- **Audio Engine**: Web Audio API with AudioWorklet processors
- **Testing**: Vitest
- **Build**: Vite

**No existing automation system detected** in the codebase.

---

## 1. Store Structure (src/state/store.ts)

### Main Store Type: `DawStore`
```
Core State:
├── Transport
│   ├── transportState: "stopped" | "playing" | "paused"
│   ├── bpm: number (20-999)
│   ├── cursorSeconds: number
│   ├── loopEnabled: boolean
│   ├── loopStart/loopEnd: number
│
├── Audio Engine
│   └── engineStatus: "uninitialized" | "suspended" | "running" | "error"
│
├── Mixer
│   └── masterVolume: number (0-2)
│
└── Tracks & Clips
    ├── tracks: readonly TrackModel[]
    ├── clips: Record<string, ClipModel>
    ├── selectedTrackIds/selectedClipIds/selectedNoteIds
```

**Key Patterns:**
- Uses Zustand for state management
- Actions are methods on the store
- No time-based parameter automation exists
- **Master volume is a single flat value** (no curves/envelopes)

---

## 2. Track System (src/state/track/types.ts)

### Track Model
```typescript
type TrackModel = {
  id: string;
  name: string;
  type: "audio" | "instrument";
  color: string;
  muted: boolean;
  solo: boolean;
  armed: boolean;
  soloIsolate: boolean;
  volume: number; // 0..2
  pan: number; // -1..1
  clipIds: readonly string[];
}
```

### Clip Types
```typescript
// Audio Clips (non-destructive references)
type AudioClipModel = {
  type: "audio";
  id: string;
  trackId: string;
  sourceId: string;
  startTime: number;
  sourceOffset: number;
  duration: number;
  gain: number; // 0..2
  fadeIn/fadeOut: number; // seconds
  name: string;
}

// MIDI Clips (note containers)
type MidiClipModel = {
  type: "midi";
  id: string;
  trackId: string;
  startTime: number;
  duration: number;
  noteEvents: readonly MIDINoteEvent[];
  name: string;
}

// Each note has: id, pitch (0-127), velocity (0-127), startTime, duration
```

**Observations:**
- Track volume/pan are **static values** (no automation)
- Clips have **static gain, fadeIn, fadeOut** (no envelope curves)
- **No automation lane structure exists**
- No parameter curves or control points stored

---

## 3. Mixer System (src/audio/mixer/)

### Mixer Architecture
